The parking brake had a buzzer that was louder than the speakers inside it, but it had an aftermarket stereo with an aux port. The cherry on top was the 22ft bed behind it. It was a monster for 18 year old me to run deliveries in, and I always I always joked to my friends saying they could take it for their drivers test.
